divs: sighting detailsmy family and i observed multiple orange lights in the evening sky traveling from east from the southwest. i counted at least 16 of these bright orange lights\orbs high in the sky lined up like a conga line. looking directly south, they started at my 2:00 position and traveled to my 11:00 position within a 5-8 minute timeframe before dissipating once each of them reached a specific location.
Summary: My family and I observed multiple orange lights in the evening sky.
